# MindfulNest — App layer

## Verification before claiming done

```bash
npm run lint && npm test && npm run test:coppa-contracts
```

## Creature canon (Arc 1)

- M1 Tessa, M2 Luna, M3 Benson, M4 Ember, **M5 Bork** (firefly), M6 Bramble
- Firestore creature id for M5 is `mo` in enums — **child-facing name is Bork**

## Module routing

- `/module/m1` … `/module/m6` — dynamic route `app/module/[moduleId].tsx`
- Never link to `/intro` or other legacy multi-screen paths

## Dev scaffold vs product

- Placeholder map (`app/index.tsx`) is not shipping UI
- Dev-only module test controls: wrap in `__DEV__`, label clearly as developer tooling
